ial applications ranging from a quantitative comparison\nbetween numerical simulations and experimental particle-image velocimetry data\nto the analysis of simulations representing a myriad of different operating\nconditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 3 Dec 2017 06:22:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Aug 2018 12:08:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-22"}
